ITV Tour De France 2011 Stage 19 Highlights (22nd July 2011) PDTV x264 AAC

Presented by Gary Imlach, Chris Boardman and Ned Boulting. Highlights of Stage 19 - Modane to Alpe-d'Huez - 109.5km. This is the stage to be frightened of. Three massive climbs, the Col du Telegraphe, the Col du Galibier - for the second time this Tour - and the finish on the fabled Alpe d'huez for the first time for three years. Commentary: Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen.
